 "blurb": "Feral Bear is TBC's stat-stick tank: the biggest health pool and armor total in the game, trading crush-blocking for sheer effective health. Uncrittable via resilience or defense, then armor and stamina forever — with the bonus that your offset pieces are cat DPS gear. This Phase 1 snapshot aggregates 342 top DPS parses from Karazhan, Gruul's Lair and Magtheridon; the highest-consensus pick is Mantle of Malorne at 79% usage.",
 "statPriorityRationale": "Bears can't block crushes, so they win by making hits small: armor cap at 35k+, a health pool warriors can't match, and agility that doubles as dodge and crit — the mitigation math is different from every other tank.",
